CostSubTLV - Class in es.tid.pce.pcep.objects.tlvs.subtlvs
All PCEP TLVs have the following format: Type: 2 bytes Length: 2 bytes Value: variable A PCEP object TLV is comprised of 2 bytes for the type, 2 bytes specifying the TLV length, and a value field.

ReqMissingTLV - Class in es.tid.pce.pcep.objects.tlvs
Represents a REQ-MISSING TLV, as defined in RFC 5440 The REQ-MISSING TLV is compliant with the PCEP TLV format defined in section 7.1 and is comprised of 2 bytes for the type, 2 bytes specifying the TLV length (length of the value portion in bytes), followed by a fixed-length value field of 4 bytes.
